Class EventConsumer

java.lang.Object
kueres.eventbus.EventConsumer
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.springframework.amqp.core.MessageListener
@Component
public class EventConsumer
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.springframework.amqp.core.MessageListener
The EventConsumer receives all events and distributes them to EventSubscribers.
